	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi guys,
<br />
<br />I was wondering if anyone would be able to point me in the right direction as far as how to read all of the buttons on the power pad as an input.  
<br />
<br />How would reading the power pad differ from reading a normal controller?
<br />
<br />Would I strobe it once, do 1 read, strobe it again and do another?
<br />
<br />Couldn't find any documentation on the subject.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

