	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There is an (old) doc about it on the main page.
<br /><a href="http://nesdev.com/powerpad.txt" class="postlink">http://nesdev.com/powerpad.txt</a>
<br />
<br />You get 2 bits per read on D3/D4, I think you strobe it once then read 8 times.  There's a code example in that doc too, but just ask if you have any problems.  I don't think many people have used it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


